metadata.name: Coffin Dance 2.0 (Dancing Pallbearers)
metadata.description:
The most famous global meme of 2020, which has become a true symbol of the COVID-19 pandemic era.

The token is issued with the support of the Ukrainian PR community, by Benjamin Aidoo team in collaboration with Matthew “DigiNeko” Ordrick, who in late March 2020 uploaded the video to YouTube which started a trend on the Internet.

The owner of this token is going to get good luck for eternity.

Format: 498 x  298 GIF
